msgstr ""
"Ovo će umetnuti gornji HTML kod unutar &lt;HEAD&gt; samo na početnoj "
"stranici."

#: application/controllers/admin/preferences.php:272
msgid "Comic Keywords"
msgstr "Ključne riječi za strip"

#: application/controllers/admin/preferences.php:278
msgid ""
"By default comic name, tags, parodies and authors will be added inside the "
"&lt;HEAD&gt; as keywords in the main comic page. If you'd like to have other"
" custom keywords, write them there. Note that each keyword must be separated"
" from the others with a comma."
msgstr ""
"Prema zadanim postavkama naziv stripa, oznake, parodije i autori bit će "
"dodani unutar &lt;HEAD&gt; kao ključne riječi na glavnoj stranici stripa. "
"Ako želite imati druge prilagođene ključne riječi, upišite ih tamo. Imajte "
"na umu da svaka ključna riječ mora biti odvojena od ostalih zarezom."

#: application/controllers/admin/preferences.php:283
msgid "Custom Navigation Link"
msgstr "Prilagođena navigacijska veza"

#: application/controllers/admin/preferences.php:289
msgid "Inserts a custom navigation link in the navigation bar."
msgstr "Umeće prilagođenu navigacijsku vezu u navigacijsku traku."

#: application/controllers/admin/preferences.php:294
msgid "Footer Text"
msgstr "Tekst podnožja"

#: application/controllers/admin/preferences.php:300
msgid ""
"Inserts the text above in the footer such as disclaimers. (Note: If the "
"content uploaded does not belong to you, do not write things like \"All "
"Rights Reserived&copy;\" above. However, if you're releasing your own works,"
" please consider using <a href=\"http://creativecommons.org/\">Creative "
"Commons Licenses</a> to protect them.)"
msgstr ""
"Umeće gornji tekst u podnožje kao što su odricanja od odgovornosti. "
"(Napomena: Ako preneseni sadržaj ne pripada vama, nemojte pisati stvari "
"poput \"Sva prava pridržana&copy;\" iznad. Međutim, ako objavljujete "
"vlastita djela, razmislite o korištenju <a "
"href=\"http://creativecommons.org/\">Creative Commons licenci</a> da ih "
"zaštitite.)"

#: application/controllers/admin/preferences.php:305
msgid "Footer Code"
msgstr "Šifra podnožja"

#: application/controllers/admin/preferences.php:311
msgid "This will insert the HTML code above after the &lt;BODY&gt;."
msgstr "Ovo će umetnuti gornji HTML kod nakon &lt;BODY&gt;."

