"pomoću vlastitog FTP softvera. Bez ovoga nećete moći instalirati ili "
"pokrenuti FoOlSlide."

#: application/controllers/install.php:335
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The %s directory needs to be writable as well. Use this command in your "
"shell if possible: %s or change its permissions recursively to 777 with your"
